553
00:38:44,572 --> 00:38:46,271
Astaga, ini tas merk terbaru.

554
00:38:46,372 --> 00:38:48,642
Terima kasih, Nn. Jiah, kau
sangat pengertian sekali.

555
00:38:49,541 --> 00:38:53,182
Aku mengira disini akan sejuk,
ternyata mataharinya sangat terik.

556
00:38:53,182 --> 00:38:54,852
Apa kita perlu pindah kesana?

557
00:38:54,852 --> 00:38:57,081
Benar, sinar UV
buruk untuk kulit.

558
00:38:57,322 --> 00:38:58,421
