untuk tak membencimu.

648
00:43:55,552 --> 00:43:57,682
Rasa lelahku tiba-tiba
saja menghilang.

649
00:44:08,262 --> 00:44:09,291
Bagus.

650
00:44:10,561 --> 00:44:11,631
Cuma kerikil.

651
00:44:13,771 --> 00:44:15,131
